title: The Favorites - CFB Week 1 Betting Preview
itunes:title: The Favorites - CFB Week 1 Betting Preview
description:
The first major slate of the college football season is this week, with matchups lasting from Thursday all the way through Labor Day evening. Here to help Chad Millman and Simon Hunter break it all down are Action Network experts Stuckey and Collin Wilson, who go through some of their favorite bets, plus a dive into Michigan and Ohio State, the College Football Player, why Collin won't speak Billy Napier's name and so much more. #Herd
